00:01:52,920 --> 00:01:55,080
[thwacking]

23
00:01:58,480 --> 00:02:00,480
[somber music]

24
00:02:07,880 --> 00:02:10,600
[Yan Zhiming] Xinglong, you're the only
aggressive player on our team.

25
00:02:11,360 --> 00:02:13,479
Please reconsider.

26
00:02:16,880 --> 00:02:18,880
[He Xinglong] I believe he will be

27
00:02:19,880 --> 00:02:22,520
a top-class professional player
if he didn't give up on tennis.

28
00:02:24,320 --> 00:02:26,040
That's what I can't achieve
in my whole life.

29
00:02:27,240 --> 00:02:29,600
But I'm kind of blessed now.

30
00:02:30,160 --> 00:02:31,200
As a high school student,

31
00:02:31,280 --> 00:02:33,080
I already have two favorite things.

32
00:02:33,960 --> 00:02:35,080
One is roasting goose.

33
00:02:35,960 --> 00:02:37,400
Burning!

34
00:02:37,480 --> 00:02:38,560
[whooshing]

35
00:02:38,640 --> 00:02:40,280
[He Xinglong] The other is playing tennis.

36
00:02:45,520 --> 00:02:46,840
But gradually, I found that

37
00:02:48,240 --> 00:02:52,280
I don't have the ability
to make them be the priorities of my life.

38
00:02:59,720 --> 00:03:01,720
[somber music]

39
00:03:09,520 --> 00:03:11,720
[somber music continues]

40
00:03:15,160 --> 00:03:16,240
Why are you here?

41
00:03:16,320 --> 00:03:17,800
Aren't you going to play today?

42
00:03:18,800 --> 00:03:20,120
Do we have a competition today?

43
00:03:20,920 --> 00:03:22,080
Don't you know?

44
00:03:23,720 --> 00:03:24,840
I have some business at home.

45
00:03:25,280 --> 00:03:26,240
I have to go. Bye.

46
00:03:41,760 --> 00:03:43,920
[thwacking]

47
00:03:46,760 --> 00:03:49,360
[Dayong] Today's training session
will be announced by the captain.

48
00:03:49,840 --> 00:03:51,440
Let's make the court tidy before that.

49
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:53,960
I have to go.
I haven't finished my homework yet.

50
00:03:54,520 --> 00:03:57,360
Picking up balls is not our job.

51
00:03:57,440 --> 00:03:59,800
[Baiyang] You have sore muscles as well.

52
00:04:00,640 --> 00:04:01,680
It won't kill you.

53
00:04:02,320 --> 00:04:03,440
But I will be tired.

54
00:04:04,320 --> 00:04:05,480
How can I practice later?

55
00:04:05,560 --> 00:04:07,440
[Weiming] Is that all the strength
you've got?

56
00:04:08,520 --> 00:04:10,520
[tense music]

57
00:04:22,959 --> 00:04:24,839
I thought you had
a busy training schedule.

58
00:04:25,680 --> 00:04:27,240
Why did you come here today

59
00:04:27,800 --> 00:04:30,040
dressed up like a group of pop singers?

60
00:04:30,360 --> 00:04:31,800
Are you here to challenge us?

61
00:04:31,880 --> 00:04:32,840
That's right.

62
00:04:33,520 --> 00:04:34,960
We are here to defeat you.

63
00:04:35,320 --> 00:04:36,240
[scoffs]

64
00:04:36,520 --> 00:04:37,840
Losers.

65
00:04:38,400 --> 00:04:39,240
You can't defeat us.

66
00:04:39,920 --> 00:04:41,320
We will beat you

67
00:04:41,760 --> 00:04:43,520
whenever it is, and wherever we are.

68
00:04:44,120 --> 00:04:45,720
[snickers]
Fine.

69
00:04:46,440 --> 00:04:47,720
Then let's have a bet.

70
00:04:48,160 --> 00:04:49,120
[scoffs]

71
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:51,520
[Baiyang] What bet?

72
00:04:51,840 --> 00:04:52,680
What bet will it be?

73
00:04:53,440 --> 00:04:54,280
If you lose,

74
00:04:54,680 --> 00:04:56,360
we want all of your team uniforms.

75
00:04:57,080 --> 00:04:58,080
[scoffs]

76
00:04:58,520 --> 00:04:59,920
You are being way too arrogant.

77
00:05:00,960 --> 00:05:01,960
Fine, then.

78
00:05:02,360 --> 00:05:03,560
Just the two of you?

79
00:05:03,880 --> 00:05:05,560
Can you represent the whole team?

80
00:05:06,160 --> 00:05:07,000
I'm in.

81
00:05:09,600 --> 00:05:11,600
[rock music]

82
00:05:21,960 --> 00:05:23,960
[rock music continues]

83
00:05:25,560 --> 00:05:26,760
I won't lose anyway.

84
00:05:26,840 --> 00:05:27,800
It doesn't matter.

85
00:05:28,280 --> 00:05:29,280
[scoffs]

86
00:05:29,960 --> 00:05:31,040
[Siyang] Is everyone here?

87
00:05:42,200 --> 00:05:43,400
For today's training,

88
00:05:43,480 --> 00:05:45,120
we will have a competition
against Yu Feng.

89
00:05:46,120 --> 00:05:48,760
I will discuss the schedule
with Captain Xu Ziping.

90
00:05:49,480 --> 00:05:50,840
Let's warm up first.

91
00:05:59,760 --> 00:06:00,720
[phone beeps]

92
00:06:06,160 --> 00:06:08,360
[Siyang] Let's meet at
and tidy up the court.

93
00:06:08,440 --> 00:06:10,720
The latecomer will have to run ten laps.
Please reply.

94
00:06:12,560 --> 00:06:13,720
[sighs]

95
00:06:13,960 --> 00:06:14,800
SIYANG

96
00:06:25,480 --> 00:06:27,480
YU QING VERSUS YU FENG
MATCH SCHEDULE

97
00:06:29,560 --> 00:06:32,320
Captain Siyang and I fixed the schedule.

98
00:06:32,760 --> 00:06:33,960
After five minutes,

99
00:06:34,360 --> 00:06:36,080
four matches will begin at the same time.

100
00:06:36,640 --> 00:06:38,760
Where is Lu Xia?
Why doesn't Lu Xia play this time?

101
00:06:38,840 --> 00:06:40,480
Focus on your own match.

102
00:06:40,840 --> 00:06:42,240
Why bother caring about others?

103
00:06:43,000 --> 00:06:44,120
[scoffs]

104
00:06:44,200 --> 00:06:46,400
We have our reasons
for the way we fixed the schedule.

105
00:06:46,840 --> 00:06:50,200
Everyone, please go to your court
and get ready according to the schedule.

106
00:06:51,520 --> 00:06:53,680
CHI DAYONG AND TANG JIALE
VERSUS CHEN DESEN AND WEI KEFEI

107
00:06:56,840 --> 00:06:58,040
[exhales heavily]

108
00:07:04,840 --> 00:07:06,800
[grunting]

109
00:07:10,520 --> 00:07:12,560
[heavy breathing]

110
00:07:13,880 --> 00:07:14,960
I'm sorry.

111
00:07:16,280 --> 00:07:19,240
They didn't get you a better partner,
so you have to stay with me.

112
00:07:21,280 --> 00:07:23,280
I have never thought
about changing my partner.

113
00:07:23,360 --> 00:07:25,360
There are so many players
who are better than me.

114
00:07:25,440 --> 00:07:27,000
Some run faster.

115
00:07:27,080 --> 00:07:28,400
Some are more hard-working.

116
00:07:28,720 --> 00:07:30,320
-And--
-Don't compare yourself to others.

117
00:07:30,800 --> 00:07:33,560
But we should
at least keep improving ourselves.

118
00:07:36,400 --> 00:07:37,840
In order to do that

119
00:07:38,400 --> 00:07:39,560
we should trust each other

120
00:07:40,160 --> 00:07:41,200
and make no secrets.

121
00:07:41,840 --> 00:07:43,840
[somber music]

122
00:07:51,400 --> 00:07:52,680
Kefei.

123
00:07:53,040 --> 00:07:55,800
It seems we can get revenge for last time.

124
00:07:57,320 --> 00:07:58,480
Dream on.

125
00:07:58,760 --> 00:08:01,960
You are far from being a match for us.

126
00:08:04,680 --> 00:08:06,480
STRENGTH SPEED DEFENSE

127
00:08:06,560 --> 00:08:07,960
ATTACK PSYCHOLOGY

128
00:08:08,520 --> 00:08:10,080
I have researched them beforehand.

129
00:08:10,320 --> 00:08:11,360
It's simple.

130
00:08:11,760 --> 00:08:14,080
[Yan Zhiming] You can follow me
and do what I tell you to do.

131
00:08:14,440 --> 00:08:15,760
I can play on my own.

132
00:08:17,040 --> 00:08:20,320
If you don't want your team uniform,
do whatever you want.

133
00:08:20,640 --> 00:08:21,920
Xingzi isn't here today.

134
00:08:22,040 --> 00:08:23,040
That's lucky for her.

135
00:08:23,640 --> 00:08:26,120
[Weiming] Because she won't see you
lose to me.

136
00:08:26,840 --> 00:08:29,040
You can say what you want.
Only the result matters.

137
00:08:29,120 --> 00:08:30,640
I heard that you have sore muscles.

138
00:08:30,720 --> 00:08:32,840
Don't use that as an excuse
when you lose later.

139
00:08:33,159 --> 00:08:34,039
[scoffs]

140
00:08:34,960 --> 00:08:36,640
Please get ready, everyone.

141
00:08:36,960 --> 00:08:37,919
[chuckles]

142
00:08:38,320 --> 00:08:40,320
[upbeat music]

143
00:08:47,520 --> 00:08:49,480
Finally, I can compete with you.

144
00:08:49,880 --> 00:08:50,960
I am looking forward to it.

145
00:09:02,400 --> 00:09:03,240
-[grunts]
-[whooshes]

146
00:09:07,560 --> 00:09:08,640
[scoffs]

147
00:09:11,640 --> 00:09:14,080
[thwacking]

148
00:09:14,840 --> 00:09:16,600
Lu Xia, we seem to have something
in common,

149
00:09:16,880 --> 00:09:18,560
even sitting on the bench now together.

150
00:09:19,520 --> 00:09:21,240
However, it's good
that you don't play today.

151
00:09:21,440 --> 00:09:22,880
You may get hurt again.

152
00:09:26,320 --> 00:09:28,400
By the way, how are your eyes?

153
00:09:28,920 --> 00:09:30,360
Can you read the blackboard in class?

154
00:09:30,640 --> 00:09:33,000
It's a big problem.
It might affect your grades.

155
00:09:33,400 --> 00:09:35,680
How about we take a vision test again?

156
00:09:35,760 --> 00:09:37,760
[playful music]

157
00:09:38,520 --> 00:09:41,400
STANDARD VISION TEST CHART

158
00:09:41,720 --> 00:09:44,160
[cellphone ringing]

159
00:09:47,440 --> 00:09:48,280
Hello, Coach.

160
00:09:49,280 --> 00:09:50,160
Yes.

161
00:09:50,560 --> 00:09:51,440
It's just begun.

162
00:09:52,720 --> 00:09:53,680
Okay.

163
00:09:53,960 --> 00:09:55,520
I'll update you when it's done.

164
00:09:56,320 --> 00:09:57,400
Mm-hm.

165
00:09:57,480 --> 00:10:00,200
[thwacking]

166
00:10:01,240 --> 00:10:02,120
-[grunts]
-[thwacks]

167
00:10:02,200 --> 00:10:03,600
[Zhuo Zhi pants]

168
00:10:03,680 --> 00:10:05,680
[tense music]

169
00:10:05,920 --> 00:10:06,960
[exhales sharply]

170
00:10:15,560 --> 00:10:16,560
[sighs]

171
00:10:16,960 --> 00:10:19,120
[Zhuo Zhi] You organized the match
to raise their morale.

172
00:10:19,520 --> 00:10:21,120
So why are you getting me involved?

173
00:10:30,400 --> 00:10:31,440
Go easy on me, will you?

174
00:10:36,200 --> 00:10:37,560
-[grunts]
-[whooshes]

175
00:10:37,880 --> 00:10:38,760
[thwacks]

176
00:10:40,160 --> 00:10:42,600
[heavy breathing]

177
00:10:45,000 --> 00:10:46,000
ZHUO ZHI VERSUS XU ZIPING

178
00:10:49,920 --> 00:10:50,840
[exhales sharply]

179
00:10:56,400 --> 00:10:57,920
[chuckles]

180
00:11:04,720 --> 00:11:05,720
[sighs sharply]

181
00:11:11,600 --> 00:11:12,760
[zooms]

182
00:11:13,360 --> 00:11:15,800
-[thwacking]
-[grunting]

183
00:11:27,600 --> 00:11:29,160
[zooms]

184
00:11:31,160 --> 00:11:32,600
[Ziping groans]

185
00:11:33,240 --> 00:11:34,240
-[grunts]
-[thwacks]

186
00:11:34,840 --> 00:11:36,160
[zooms]

187
00:11:39,840 --> 00:11:41,840
[upbeat music]

188
00:11:44,840 --> 00:11:46,120
[whirring]

189
00:11:47,400 --> 00:11:48,360
[groans]

190
00:11:50,240 --> 00:11:51,280
[gasps]

191
00:11:51,880 --> 00:11:53,240
This is actually interesting.

192
00:11:58,240 --> 00:11:59,200
[grunts]

193
00:12:00,600 --> 00:12:02,560
-[screaming]
-[man 1] Call an ambulance!

194
00:12:03,520 --> 00:12:04,400
[Zhuo Zhi] I am fine.

195
00:12:05,240 --> 00:12:07,240
[ominous music]

196
00:12:07,760 --> 00:12:09,560
[sighs]
What about you?

197
00:12:10,600 --> 00:12:11,560
Are you okay?

198
00:12:14,600 --> 00:12:15,640
Let's continue.

199
00:12:17,800 --> 00:12:20,200
[distant thwacking]

200
00:12:24,680 --> 00:12:26,680
[tense music]

201
00:12:27,240 --> 00:12:29,280
-[screaming]
-[man 1] It's only a tennis match.

202
00:12:29,360 --> 00:12:30,400
He went too far.

203
00:12:30,480 --> 00:12:31,600
[man 2] That's right.

204
00:12:32,520 --> 00:12:34,320
[screaming continues]

205
00:12:39,840 --> 00:12:41,840
[tense music]

206
00:12:53,640 --> 00:12:55,640
[tense music continues]

207
00:13:03,440 --> 00:13:04,360
[sighs]

208
00:13:09,120 --> 00:13:10,280
I give up.

209
00:13:10,960 --> 00:13:12,320
[gasps]

210
00:13:14,800 --> 00:13:15,960
[sighs sharply]

211
00:13:18,520 --> 00:13:19,920
[gasping]

212
00:13:23,600 --> 00:13:24,440
[sighs]

213
00:13:31,200 --> 00:13:32,160
Let's see the results.

214
00:13:34,000 --> 00:13:35,880
A Group doubles, Yu Feng won.

215
00:13:37,240 --> 00:13:40,000
[Xiuwen] B Group doubles, Yu Feng won.

216
00:13:40,720 --> 00:13:43,240
-[Mu] D Group singles, Yu Feng won.
-[both chuckling]

217
00:13:43,760 --> 00:13:46,440
[Huang Jing] E Group singles,
Yu Feng gave up.

218
00:13:56,360 --> 00:13:57,200
Okay.

219
00:13:57,640 --> 00:13:58,560
Yu Feng won.

220
00:13:59,080 --> 00:14:00,160
Take off your uniforms.

221
00:14:00,760 --> 00:14:02,760
[somber music]

222
00:14:08,000 --> 00:14:09,520
-Seriously?
-Of course.

223
00:14:10,520 --> 00:14:11,520
We were just joking.

224
00:14:11,600 --> 00:14:13,440
-You don't need to--
-Since we agreed to it,

225
00:14:13,520 --> 00:14:14,680
we must do it.

226
00:14:17,880 --> 00:14:20,040
Zhuo Zhi didn't lose.
He doesn't need to take it off.

227
00:14:20,120 --> 00:14:21,360
We lost as a team.

228
00:14:21,680 --> 00:14:23,520
We have to accept the fact that we lost.

229
00:14:27,440 --> 00:14:28,440
[sighs]

230
00:14:32,360 --> 00:14:33,280
Oh.

231
00:14:33,400 --> 00:14:35,400
[somber music]

232
00:14:47,440 --> 00:14:49,440
[somber music continues]

233
00:14:57,720 --> 00:14:59,080
Your uniforms stink.

234
00:14:59,160 --> 00:15:00,840
Are you going to let Xingzi wash them?

235
00:15:01,920 --> 00:15:05,440
Also, Lu Xia didn't play for the match.
It's hard for you to accept the defeat.

236
00:15:05,840 --> 00:15:07,400
I can't change the result even if I won.

237
00:15:10,880 --> 00:15:12,760
Everyone, do 50 laps each.

238
00:15:24,000 --> 00:15:25,400
I will see you off.

239
00:15:25,480 --> 00:15:26,400
Mm-hm.

240
00:15:29,280 --> 00:15:32,360
The stunt you used just now was great.

241
00:15:33,000 --> 00:15:34,600
I think we are in good condition today.

242
00:15:34,680 --> 00:15:36,400
-Yes, Let's buy a drink there.
-[Desen] Okay.

243
00:15:36,920 --> 00:15:39,360
-[Kefei] What drink do you want?
-[Desen] Coke.

244
00:15:39,440 --> 00:15:41,840
-Thank you.
-Forget it.

245
00:15:42,040 --> 00:15:43,680
It was hard work putting on a show.

246
00:15:44,360 --> 00:15:45,480
Nevertheless,

247
00:15:45,560 --> 00:15:47,080
since we have accepted this,

248
00:15:47,800 --> 00:15:48,880
like I said,

249
00:15:49,240 --> 00:15:50,520
I will not return it so easily.

250
00:15:51,000 --> 00:15:51,840
Okay.

251
00:15:52,080 --> 00:15:53,800
We will win it back by our strength.

252
00:15:54,120 --> 00:15:56,680
I will talk to Mr. Qi
about the training between two schools.

253
00:15:57,280 --> 00:15:59,080
-See you then.
-[Ziping] Mm-hm.

254
00:16:04,240 --> 00:16:06,360
[Siyang] I did expect them to be
in a bad condition,

255
00:16:06,760 --> 00:16:08,400
but I didn't expect them to lose so much.

256
00:16:10,520 --> 00:16:11,520
Everyone, gather around.

257
00:16:19,040 --> 00:16:20,120
From what I remember,

258
00:16:20,800 --> 00:16:22,680
this isn't the first time
you lost recently.

259
00:16:23,880 --> 00:16:26,080
Losing is not a frightening thing.

260
00:16:26,880 --> 00:16:29,400
What's terrifying is
that we can't learn the lesson from it.

261
00:16:30,200 --> 00:16:32,600
Recently, the coach and I
have not been around.

262
00:16:33,400 --> 00:16:34,640
Many things are going on now.

263
00:16:35,560 --> 00:16:37,040
But I hope you can remember

264
00:16:37,760 --> 00:16:42,000
why you insisted on training every day and
participating in a competition back then.

265
00:16:43,080 --> 00:16:44,320
As the top players of Yu Qing,

266
00:16:45,000 --> 00:16:46,080
you should take pride

267
00:16:46,600 --> 00:16:47,880
and be responsible

268
00:16:48,320 --> 00:16:49,640
instead of showing off.

269
00:16:51,200 --> 00:16:55,120
It is my dream to lead us
to the national league.

270
00:16:55,600 --> 00:16:57,720
But I can't do that on my own.

271
00:16:59,520 --> 00:17:01,640
[Siyang] I don't want to
have to force anyone either.

272
00:17:02,400 --> 00:17:04,119
You can make your own choices.

273
00:17:05,280 --> 00:17:06,839
But when you make the choice,

274
00:17:07,760 --> 00:17:10,520
I hope you can be responsible
for making such a choice.

275
00:17:11,680 --> 00:17:13,599
The future matches will be even fiercer.

276
00:17:14,480 --> 00:17:16,200
You should know

277
00:17:17,200 --> 00:17:18,560
that you will lose for sure

278
00:17:19,560 --> 00:17:20,640
if this condition continues.

279
00:17:21,200 --> 00:17:22,760
If you don't understand what I'm saying,

280
00:17:23,680 --> 00:17:25,000
you'd better give up right now.

281
00:17:26,720 --> 00:17:28,400
I will give you a chance to choose.

282
00:17:29,480 --> 00:17:30,720
Those who want to continue

283
00:17:31,200 --> 00:17:33,840
can meet at the Qingniaotai Station
on the day after tomorrow.

284
00:17:34,600 --> 00:17:37,720
The coach has arranged a training session
with Yu Feng outside school.

285
00:17:39,120 --> 00:17:40,400
Those who don't want to continue

286
00:17:41,200 --> 00:17:42,440
may give up right now.

287
00:17:43,080 --> 00:17:44,800
That's all. You can go.

288
00:17:53,320 --> 00:17:54,200
[sighs]

289
00:17:54,360 --> 00:17:56,560
-[Huang Jing] Qingniaotai. Qingniaotai.
-[Mu gasping]

290
00:17:56,880 --> 00:17:59,200
QIngniaotai. I am blessed
with this opportunity.

291
00:17:59,880 --> 00:18:01,560
-What's wrong with you?
-[moans, pants]

292
00:18:01,920 --> 00:18:02,920
This is our chance.

293
00:18:03,000 --> 00:18:06,160
The captain just said that the opportunity
is for those brave enough to work hard.

294
00:18:06,600 --> 00:18:08,600
[comical music]

295
00:18:08,680 --> 00:18:10,640
He didn't say that.

296
00:18:12,800 --> 00:18:14,880
[murmuring]

297
00:18:18,440 --> 00:18:19,320
Okay.

298
00:18:22,880 --> 00:18:23,960
Hmm?

299
00:18:27,040 --> 00:18:29,360
GOLD MEDAL ROAST GOOSE
SUCCULENT AND DELICIOUS

300
00:18:32,280 --> 00:18:33,120
[Xinglong grunts]

301
00:18:35,720 --> 00:18:36,840
[blowing air]

302
00:18:40,240 --> 00:18:41,440
[sighs]

303
00:18:46,800 --> 00:18:47,640
Xinglong.

304
00:18:49,600 --> 00:18:51,360
[gasps]
Dad.

305
00:18:52,000 --> 00:18:53,120
Why don't you use the mop?

306
00:18:54,120 --> 00:18:56,400
Dad, I've mopped twice already.

307
00:18:56,480 --> 00:18:58,760
This is the third step.

308
00:18:58,840 --> 00:18:59,760
[chuckles]

309
00:18:59,840 --> 00:19:00,920
That's not necessary.

310
00:19:01,200 --> 00:19:03,040
It will be dirty again
when the guests arrive.

311
00:19:04,080 --> 00:19:04,960
Dad.

312
00:19:05,040 --> 00:19:06,960
We'll be inspected tomorrow
for hygiene rating.

313
00:19:07,280 --> 00:19:09,720
If we always clean this place like this,

314
00:19:10,320 --> 00:19:12,040
we will get a better rating.

315
00:19:12,320 --> 00:19:14,200
[sighing]

316
00:19:15,360 --> 00:19:16,360
This place is shiny.

317
00:19:16,920 --> 00:19:18,320
This time, we'll get the top rating.

318
00:19:18,400 --> 00:19:19,240
[both chuckle]

319
00:19:19,360 --> 00:19:20,200
Okay, my son.

320
00:19:20,480 --> 00:19:22,440
-I will go to the kitchen then.
-Okay.

321
00:19:23,200 --> 00:19:24,560
[sighs]

322
00:19:24,640 --> 00:19:25,680
[both chuckle]

323
00:19:26,920 --> 00:19:27,920
[groans]

324
00:19:44,880 --> 00:19:45,960
[exhales sharply]

325
00:19:46,600 --> 00:19:48,400
[Huang Jing] A Group doubles, Yu Feng won.

326
00:19:49,240 --> 00:19:51,880
[Xiuwen] B Group doubles, Yu Feng won.

327
00:19:52,600 --> 00:19:55,320
-[Mu] D Group singles, Yu Feng won.
-[PA announcer] We are approaching

328
00:19:55,400 --> 00:19:56,640
the station. Please get ready...

329
00:19:56,720 --> 00:19:58,920
[Huang Jing] E Group singles,
Yu Feng gave up.

330
00:20:02,920 --> 00:20:05,960
THE NEXT TRAIN IS TEN STATIONS AWAY

331
00:20:06,480 --> 00:20:08,480
[somber music]

332
00:20:20,280 --> 00:20:22,240
[Siyang] Losing is not
a frightening thing.

333
00:20:23,000 --> 00:20:25,360
What's terrifying is that
we can't learn the lesson from it.

334
00:20:36,040 --> 00:20:37,360
Australian formation.

335
00:20:39,800 --> 00:20:41,200
Double up-front formation.

336
00:20:43,760 --> 00:20:44,880
[exhales sharply]

337
00:20:44,960 --> 00:20:46,280
[gasping]

338
00:20:47,560 --> 00:20:49,480
[shouting]
What can I do by myself?

339
00:20:52,800 --> 00:20:53,720
[grunts]

340
00:20:55,800 --> 00:20:57,000
[sighs]

341
00:20:58,320 --> 00:21:02,360
[Siyang] It is my dream to lead us
to the national league.

342
00:21:02,760 --> 00:21:04,960
But I can't do that on my own.

343
00:21:05,240 --> 00:21:06,920
You can make your own choices.

344
00:21:08,040 --> 00:21:09,600
But when you make the choice,

345
00:21:10,680 --> 00:21:13,440
I hope you can be responsible
for making such a choice.

346
00:21:14,520 --> 00:21:16,760
The future matches will be even fiercer.

347
00:21:17,280 --> 00:21:18,880
You should know

348
00:21:19,920 --> 00:21:21,280
that you will lose for sure

349
00:21:22,320 --> 00:21:23,880
-if this condition continues.
-[scoffs]

350
00:21:24,920 --> 00:21:26,920
[somber music]

351
00:21:32,800 --> 00:21:33,720
Eat this.

352
00:21:37,840 --> 00:21:38,720
Eat it.

353
00:21:40,480 --> 00:21:42,000
I can eat by myself.

354
00:21:44,760 --> 00:21:45,680
[slurps]

355
00:21:50,360 --> 00:21:51,640
Why do you keep looking at me?

356
00:21:53,120 --> 00:21:54,760
Didn't you have a competition
with Yu Feng?

357
00:21:54,840 --> 00:21:55,840
How was it?

358
00:21:56,120 --> 00:21:56,960
We lost.

359
00:21:58,240 --> 00:21:59,360
Lost to their captain?

360
00:22:01,120 --> 00:22:02,120
Our entire team lost.

361
00:22:04,960 --> 00:22:05,840
You...

362
00:22:08,160 --> 00:22:09,600
Xu Ziping is really excellent.

363
00:22:09,680 --> 00:22:10,680
I almost lost as well.

364
00:22:14,880 --> 00:22:17,840
Does it really mean nothing to you
whether you win or not?

365
00:22:19,200 --> 00:22:20,160
It's okay.

366
00:22:20,560 --> 00:22:22,040
Eat. The food is getting cold.

367
00:22:24,120 --> 00:22:26,480
Let's see who finishes first. Okay?

368
00:22:29,960 --> 00:22:31,960
You won. I'm full.

369
00:22:35,960 --> 00:22:37,160
[sighs sharply]

370
00:22:40,400 --> 00:22:42,400
[dramatic music]

371
00:22:43,040 --> 00:22:45,160
YU QING

372
00:22:47,880 --> 00:22:49,160
[panting]

373
00:22:54,800 --> 00:22:56,120
You won again.

374
00:23:00,880 --> 00:23:01,720
[grunts]

375
00:23:03,360 --> 00:23:04,200
Don't worry.

376
00:23:05,040 --> 00:23:06,880
This is definitely the last lap.

377
00:23:07,640 --> 00:23:09,240
[Xiuwen] Does he run every day?

378
00:23:09,800 --> 00:23:11,120
He's been running the most today.

379
00:23:14,520 --> 00:23:16,880
[heavy breathing]

380
00:23:19,640 --> 00:23:21,120
He isn't crazy, is he?

381
00:23:26,680 --> 00:23:28,720
-[computer beeping]
-[keyboard clacking]

382
00:23:32,600 --> 00:23:33,880
YAN ZHIMING
MU SIYANG

383
00:23:33,960 --> 00:23:35,040
ZHUO ZHI
QIAO CHEN

384
00:23:35,320 --> 00:23:36,640
[beeping continues]

385
00:23:36,720 --> 00:23:37,840
[sighs]

386
00:23:44,080 --> 00:23:46,240
ZHANG BAIYANG, TANG JIALE
CHI DAYONG

387
00:23:50,320 --> 00:23:51,360
[beeping stops]

388
00:23:51,880 --> 00:23:53,000
[sighs]

389
00:23:53,400 --> 00:23:55,320
[Yan Zhiming] It seems that
Murphy's law is right.

390
00:23:55,400 --> 00:23:57,480
No matter how improbable it is
for things to get worse,

391
00:23:57,560 --> 00:23:58,760
it gets worse anyway.

392
00:24:03,040 --> 00:24:04,760
[man 3] Don't forget.
There is Maxwell's law.

393
00:24:04,840 --> 00:24:07,200
Anything turns out better than expected.

394
00:24:07,280 --> 00:24:11,160
Things will get better
when the time is ripe.

395
00:24:16,040 --> 00:24:18,040
[somber music]

396
00:24:19,200 --> 00:24:20,120
[phone beeps]

397
00:24:27,280 --> 00:24:28,720
[Lu Xia's mom] Did you make a choice?

398
00:24:34,640 --> 00:24:35,520
Hi, son.

399
00:24:35,720 --> 00:24:37,200
Do you want to come and live with me?

400
00:24:37,800 --> 00:24:39,520
Your father has agreed.

401
00:24:39,960 --> 00:24:41,120
-This way.
-[man 4] Thank you.

402
00:24:41,200 --> 00:24:42,080
Goodbye.

403
00:24:42,480 --> 00:24:43,440
Come back anytime.

404
00:24:43,520 --> 00:24:44,600
Thank you.

405
00:24:45,400 --> 00:24:48,000
-[woman 1] It is a great restaurant.
-[man 4] I am glad you like it.

406
00:24:48,080 --> 00:24:49,040
[woman 1 chuckles]

407
00:24:52,400 --> 00:24:53,960
Hello, Captain Siyang from Yu Qing.

408
00:24:54,520 --> 00:24:55,440
Hello, sir.

409
00:24:55,880 --> 00:24:57,400
Do you want takeout for your family?

410
00:24:57,720 --> 00:25:00,200
Uh, no, sir.
I will have meals here next time.

411
00:25:00,280 --> 00:25:02,360
-[Mr. He chuckles]
-I am here to talk to you

412
00:25:02,440 --> 00:25:04,240
about He Xinglong.

413
00:25:06,120 --> 00:25:07,160
He dropped out of the team.

414
00:25:07,480 --> 00:25:08,360
Did you know?

415
00:25:09,120 --> 00:25:09,960
He dropped out?

416
00:25:10,560 --> 00:25:11,400
Yes.

417
00:25:12,920 --> 00:25:14,920
[somber music]

418
00:25:22,520 --> 00:25:24,040
TENNIS HOME FOR TEENAGERS

419
00:25:24,120 --> 00:25:25,240
[sighs sharply]

420
00:25:27,000 --> 00:25:27,960
[clicks tongue]

421
00:25:31,760 --> 00:25:32,960
What's that in your hand?

422
00:25:34,520 --> 00:25:35,440
This...

423
00:25:35,800 --> 00:25:37,520
Peng Xiang bought it
for the cheering squad.

424
00:25:37,880 --> 00:25:39,320
Do you want to have a try?

425
00:25:41,240 --> 00:25:42,440
-This?
-Uh-huh.

426
00:25:42,520 --> 00:25:44,040
Can I become handsome if I use it?

427
00:25:44,120 --> 00:25:45,320
[Xiuwen] Of course.

428
00:25:47,840 --> 00:25:49,240
[Siyang] Only the three of you came?

429
00:25:49,800 --> 00:25:51,560
-Captain.
-Captain Siyang.

430
00:25:52,480 --> 00:25:53,600
-Yes.
-Captain.

431
00:25:54,240 --> 00:25:55,160
Then...

432
00:25:55,640 --> 00:25:57,320
Maybe the others missed the bus.

433
00:25:57,400 --> 00:25:58,400
Let's wait.

434
00:26:02,800 --> 00:26:05,120
The time's up. We don't have to wait.

435
00:26:07,920 --> 00:26:10,800
Then shall we return home?

436
00:26:11,600 --> 00:26:14,400
We'll proceed with the training.
I will take you to the hotel.

437
00:26:14,720 --> 00:26:15,840
Follow me.

438
00:26:20,080 --> 00:26:21,080
[sighs]

439
00:26:35,400 --> 00:26:37,360
-Yan?
-They are all here.

440
00:26:37,440 --> 00:26:38,400
They are cleaning up.

441
00:26:38,960 --> 00:26:39,880
It will take...

442
00:26:40,240 --> 00:26:42,000
31 minutes 44 seconds.

443
00:26:42,480 --> 00:26:44,440
Cleaning up? Cleaning what?

444
00:26:44,520 --> 00:26:45,960
Everyone arrived early.

445
00:26:46,040 --> 00:26:48,240
We had a bet with Yu Feng on cleaning.

446
00:26:49,880 --> 00:26:53,440
Whichever team loses,
the team has to eat only rice today.

447
00:26:54,880 --> 00:26:56,760
How can they eat only rice?

448
00:26:57,120 --> 00:27:00,080
-[Ying] Training is so tiring.
-Anyway, the rice is more than enough.

449
00:27:00,480 --> 00:27:03,080
If you want to eat something better,
then clean hard.

450
00:27:03,160 --> 00:27:05,160
[comical music]

451
00:27:05,560 --> 00:27:07,240
-Rice?
-How can we eat only rice?

452
00:27:07,320 --> 00:27:08,720
-Training is so tiring.
-[sobs]

453
00:27:08,800 --> 00:27:10,560
I don't want to eat only rice.

454
00:27:10,640 --> 00:27:12,800
-I'll lose my muscles if I eat only rice.
-Okay.

455
00:27:13,080 --> 00:27:13,920
Let's go.

456
00:27:14,000 --> 00:27:16,120
[Xiuwen sobbing]
Rice...

457
00:27:19,600 --> 00:27:20,440
Dad.

458
00:27:21,480 --> 00:27:24,000
Aren't the hygiene inspectors here yet?
I'll clean some more.

459
00:27:24,360 --> 00:27:25,480
You don't have to.

460
00:27:25,560 --> 00:27:26,960
We'll do without a top rating.

461
00:27:31,360 --> 00:27:32,880
[chuckles]
Okay, then.

462
00:27:32,960 --> 00:27:35,520
Then we'll do better next year.

463
00:27:35,600 --> 00:27:36,800
[groans]
No need for that.

464
00:27:38,480 --> 00:27:41,520
I heard that your team
went to train, right?

465
00:27:42,160 --> 00:27:43,600
[nervous chuckle]

466
00:27:44,880 --> 00:27:47,800
Why are you still here?
Aren't you going to go with them?

467
00:27:49,160 --> 00:27:51,160
[dramatic music]

468
00:27:52,000 --> 00:27:53,120
Uh...

469
00:27:54,240 --> 00:27:55,600
I want to stay and help you.

470
00:27:56,720 --> 00:27:57,640
Okay.

471
00:27:58,400 --> 00:28:01,560
Go and deliver the food.
The orders are from the company next door.

472
00:28:02,680 --> 00:28:03,600
Okay.

473
00:28:04,040 --> 00:28:05,960
[Mr. He sighs sharply]

474
00:28:12,880 --> 00:28:14,280
TENNIS HOME FOR TEENAGERS

475
00:28:14,360 --> 00:28:16,160
[Qiao Chen] We even lost
the match in cleaning.

476
00:28:20,760 --> 00:28:23,120
[munching]

477
00:28:32,320 --> 00:28:33,560
[Kefei] What are you doing?

478
00:28:34,320 --> 00:28:36,320
[comical music]

479
00:28:37,680 --> 00:28:38,800
[clears throat]

480
00:28:39,760 --> 00:28:41,160
[chuckling]

481
00:28:46,680 --> 00:28:48,200
Let's increase the amount of training.

482
00:28:49,720 --> 00:28:51,680
I don't want to lose any more next time.

483
00:28:52,280 --> 00:28:53,360
To be specific,

484
00:28:53,640 --> 00:28:56,880
if we multiply the training amount
by 2.34 percent, our chance of winning--

485
00:28:56,960 --> 00:28:59,360
You don't need to analyze it.
I will train four times as much.

486
00:28:59,800 --> 00:29:00,720
Starting tomorrow.

487
00:29:05,440 --> 00:29:06,800
I will train five times as much.

488
00:29:10,560 --> 00:29:13,120
[munching continues]

489
00:29:18,440 --> 00:29:20,480
[crickets chirping]

490
00:29:24,840 --> 00:29:26,320
-Siyang.
-[Siyang] Coach.

491
00:29:27,600 --> 00:29:29,760
I have something to discuss with you.

492
00:29:31,160 --> 00:29:33,000
If it's about you using your left hand,

493
00:29:33,560 --> 00:29:34,880
then there is nothing to discuss.

494
00:29:35,280 --> 00:29:36,200
The thing is...

495
00:29:36,640 --> 00:29:37,640
Recently,

496
00:29:38,040 --> 00:29:39,960
I feel that my left hand
has become much better.

497
00:29:40,280 --> 00:29:41,880
Also, everyone is so rarely enthusiastic.

498
00:29:43,120 --> 00:29:45,760
What about your right hand?
Can you use it as well as your left hand?

499
00:29:46,240 --> 00:29:47,880
I'm not used to playing
with my right hand.

500
00:29:48,360 --> 00:29:51,960
I can never use my right hand as well
as my left no matter how hard I try.

501
00:29:53,520 --> 00:29:55,360
[sighs]
Siyang.

502
00:29:55,920 --> 00:29:58,200
Forget it.

503
00:29:59,360 --> 00:30:01,640
I won't allow you to use your left hand.

504
00:30:04,720 --> 00:30:06,120
[gasps, stutters]

505
00:30:06,200 --> 00:30:08,720
-[retreating footsteps]
-[sighs]

506
00:30:15,800 --> 00:30:16,880
TRAINING PLAN

507
00:30:16,960 --> 00:30:18,520
YU QING HIGH SCHOOL TENNIS CLUB

508
00:30:18,600 --> 00:30:20,920
CONTENTS: LIFTING DUMBBELLS,
PUSH-UPS, SWING PRACTICE

509
00:30:21,440 --> 00:30:23,280
[birds chirping]

510
00:30:24,720 --> 00:30:26,400
Yu Qing team hasn't finished cleaning.

511
00:30:26,480 --> 00:30:28,120
They already started training.

512
00:30:30,240 --> 00:30:32,400
VOLLEY TRAINING
SIT-UPS

513
00:30:32,480 --> 00:30:34,360
Wining in cleaning doesn't mean anything.

514
00:30:34,680 --> 00:30:35,880
We won't lose in training.

515
00:30:36,200 --> 00:30:37,280
Let's go.

516
00:30:37,760 --> 00:30:38,600
Okay.

517
00:30:41,240 --> 00:30:43,240
[upbeat music]

518
00:30:43,480 --> 00:30:44,680
Come on. Gain some strength.

519
00:30:46,240 --> 00:30:48,240
The next part is swing training.
Thirty rounds each.

520
00:30:48,320 --> 00:30:49,480
Forehand and backhand swing.

521
00:30:49,560 --> 00:30:50,600
[Mu] Three groups in total.

522
00:30:50,680 --> 00:30:52,360
Multiply that by 4, and we have 12 groups.

523
00:30:52,440 --> 00:30:54,240
We're to train both in mornings
and afternoons.

524
00:30:54,320 --> 00:30:55,360
Six groups in the morning.

525
00:30:55,840 --> 00:30:58,480
Can we finish before lunch
if we go on like this?

526
00:30:59,160 --> 00:31:00,800
We need to step up.

527
00:31:01,160 --> 00:31:02,520
[Mu] I'm sick of eating only rice.

528
00:31:04,200 --> 00:31:05,560
Lu Xia, don't you need more rest?

529
00:31:05,640 --> 00:31:06,960
I have a lot of catching up to do.

530
00:31:07,080 --> 00:31:08,160
[Qiao Chen groaning]

531
00:31:12,120 --> 00:31:13,520
[groaning continues]

532
00:31:17,880 --> 00:31:20,120
Can't you keep quiet? You are too noisy.

533
00:31:20,760 --> 00:31:23,720
What's wrong with you?
I need to yell out to feel better.

534
00:31:24,040 --> 00:31:26,320
If you can't hold on anymore,
you can rest somewhere else.

535
00:31:28,320 --> 00:31:29,800
According to Baiyang's data,

536
00:31:29,880 --> 00:31:32,200
the incremental plan today
is indeed too much.

537
00:31:33,160 --> 00:31:35,320
[Yan Zhiming] I suggest that you give up
the 100 push-ups

538
00:31:35,400 --> 00:31:37,560
or you won't be able to finish
the pull-ups.

539
00:31:37,840 --> 00:31:38,760
[clicks tongue]

540
00:31:39,400 --> 00:31:40,720
Hear that?

541
00:31:41,640 --> 00:31:42,520
You know what?

542
00:31:42,760 --> 00:31:45,560
You'll have to renew my data
starting today.

543
00:31:46,280 --> 00:31:48,760
[Baiyang] And you had better be quiet.

544
00:31:48,840 --> 00:31:49,960
You are really annoying.

545
00:31:50,360 --> 00:31:51,360
[chuckles]

546
00:31:54,840 --> 00:31:57,160
If you yell like that,

547
00:31:57,240 --> 00:31:59,160
it will make it hard for you
to catch your breath.

548
00:31:59,240 --> 00:32:01,160
It will cost too much of your strength
too early,

549
00:32:01,240 --> 00:32:02,200
and cause stitches.

550
00:32:03,080 --> 00:32:03,920
[scoffs]

551
00:32:05,880 --> 00:32:09,240
[groaning]

552
00:32:10,640 --> 00:32:12,480
[panting]

553
00:32:13,600 --> 00:32:14,840
What's next?

554
00:32:15,280 --> 00:32:16,120
Rally drill.

555
00:32:16,600 --> 00:32:18,160
Do you want to rest before it starts?

556
00:32:18,720 --> 00:32:19,680
No.

557
00:32:20,680 --> 00:32:22,880
You told Jiale to rest,
but you never rest yourself.

558
00:32:22,960 --> 00:32:24,320
I am the team's anchorman.

559
00:32:24,920 --> 00:32:26,480
I should shoulder my responsibilities.

560
00:32:26,920 --> 00:32:28,960
[Dayong] We lost the previous matches
because of me.

561
00:32:42,400 --> 00:32:44,360
Okay. You can go now.

562
00:32:44,680 --> 00:32:46,600
We will meet at the dining hall
at lunchtime.

563
00:32:48,720 --> 00:32:49,560
[sighs]

564
00:32:50,040 --> 00:32:52,280
What? Do you want to continue?

565
00:32:56,160 --> 00:32:57,000
Mm-hm.

566
00:32:59,240 --> 00:33:00,360
[exhales sharply]

567
00:33:05,360 --> 00:33:07,640
[Tang Jiale groans]

568
00:33:08,720 --> 00:33:10,720
-[Xiuwen] Are you okay?
-I am fine.

569
00:33:11,200 --> 00:33:12,880
[gasps]
How many do I have left?

570
00:33:13,200 --> 00:33:14,840
There are still 135 to go.

571
00:33:15,280 --> 00:33:16,200
Huh?

572
00:33:17,520 --> 00:33:18,440
[groans]

573
00:33:18,880 --> 00:33:20,960
Jiale, are you okay?

574
00:33:22,200 --> 00:33:23,440
[grunts]

575
00:33:26,360 --> 00:33:27,440
Of course, I am.

576
00:33:31,640 --> 00:33:34,320
Vice-Captain, have you finished training?

577
00:33:34,760 --> 00:33:35,640
Mm-hm.

578
00:33:35,720 --> 00:33:37,080
I came by to see how you are doing.

579
00:33:37,360 --> 00:33:38,720
Xiuwen, let's go.

580
00:33:39,080 --> 00:33:40,520
-Uh...
-[Tang Jiale gasps]

581
00:33:42,440 --> 00:33:43,680
How many groups are left?

582
00:33:45,560 --> 00:33:47,920
If we take the penalty amount
into account,

583
00:33:48,000 --> 00:33:50,600
he needs to do 135 times more
to complete the session.

584
00:33:55,360 --> 00:33:56,680
Just do the basic amount.

585
00:33:57,320 --> 00:33:58,800
Strength is your weakness.

586
00:33:59,240 --> 00:34:00,840
If you get hurt because you overdo it,

587
00:34:01,400 --> 00:34:03,600
you can't finish the basic training.

588
00:34:04,400 --> 00:34:05,760
-Xiuwen.
-Hmm?

589
00:34:06,360 --> 00:34:07,480
Go and get the first aid kit.

590
00:34:07,560 --> 00:34:08,639
-Okay.
-There's no need.

591
00:34:09,280 --> 00:34:11,400
It's nothing serious.

592
00:34:16,239 --> 00:34:17,480
-[thuds]
-[grunts]

593
00:34:20,159 --> 00:34:21,080
-[thuds]
-[grunts]

594
00:34:23,760 --> 00:34:25,040
[man 3] How's the training going?

595
00:34:25,120 --> 00:34:28,520
[Baiyang grunting]

596
00:34:34,000 --> 00:34:35,360
[grunting continues]

597
00:34:42,239 --> 00:34:44,639
You lack strength
both in your upper arm and forearm.

598
00:34:44,920 --> 00:34:47,000
[Yan Zhiming] You put too much pressure
on your wrist.

599
00:34:47,440 --> 00:34:48,800
Your center of gravity is unstable.

600
00:34:49,239 --> 00:34:51,560
Can you stop bothering me?

601
00:34:53,199 --> 00:34:54,120
-[grunts]
-[thuds]

602
00:34:54,760 --> 00:34:57,560
By training more, you want to improve
your Boomerang Snake, right?

603
00:34:58,080 --> 00:34:59,040
[grunts]

604
00:34:59,960 --> 00:35:03,680
But the training method you are using now
is neither scientific nor efficient.

605
00:35:04,000 --> 00:35:06,520
Why not try lifting more
of your arms when swinging?

606
00:35:07,120 --> 00:35:08,680
I will do it my way.

607
00:35:08,760 --> 00:35:10,240
[grunts]
It's none of your business!

608
00:35:12,600 --> 00:35:16,640
My suggestions come from
the data analysis.

609
00:35:17,720 --> 00:35:21,040
It will definitely be more efficient
than your way.

610
00:35:21,640 --> 00:35:23,960
You say I'm using my strength
the wrong and inefficient way.

611
00:35:24,560 --> 00:35:26,960
But if I keep training,
I will succeed one day.

612
00:35:27,720 --> 00:35:30,680
You care about data all the time.

613
00:35:32,240 --> 00:35:34,160
But if one day your data tells you

614
00:35:34,480 --> 00:35:36,480
you can't win the match anyway,

615
00:35:37,280 --> 00:35:39,040
will you surrender then?

616
00:35:39,360 --> 00:35:40,520
Will you?

617
00:35:40,600 --> 00:35:43,400
I'll find out the weaknesses
of our opponents before every match.

618
00:35:44,160 --> 00:35:45,800
I always prepare you well for the matches.

619
00:35:46,360 --> 00:35:47,200
[scoffs]

620
00:35:47,280 --> 00:35:49,400
But we lost in the last match
with Yu Feng.

621
00:35:49,480 --> 00:35:52,280
That's because you didn't
follow my instructions,

622
00:35:53,120 --> 00:35:54,200
just like now.

623
00:35:56,840 --> 00:35:58,920
[pants]

624
00:36:01,400 --> 00:36:02,640
Lifting the forearm?

625
00:36:08,280 --> 00:36:09,680
-[grunts]
-[thumps]

626
00:36:10,040 --> 00:36:12,040
