627
00:36:13,440 --> 00:36:14,880
I knew I shouldn't listen to you.

628
00:36:22,840 --> 00:36:23,920
[thwacks]

629
00:36:24,840 --> 00:36:25,680
[sighs]

630
00:36:28,400 --> 00:36:29,840
-[thwacks]
-[whooshes]

631
00:36:32,080 --> 00:36:34,480
[heavy breathing]

632
00:36:34,560 --> 00:36:35,960
[thwacks]

633
00:36:41,120 --> 00:36:41,960
-[grunts]
-[thwacks]

634
00:36:44,800 --> 00:36:45,960
[exhales sharply]

635
00:36:53,720 --> 00:36:55,720
[somber music]

636
00:37:04,960 --> 00:37:06,280
-[thwacks]
-[whooshes]

637
00:37:07,680 --> 00:37:09,960
[breathes heavily]

638
00:37:14,640 --> 00:37:16,200
The coach separated you from others

639
00:37:16,680 --> 00:37:18,320
to make you practice with your right hand.

640
00:37:19,640 --> 00:37:20,560
Why?

641
00:37:23,200 --> 00:37:24,120
It's nothing.

642
00:37:25,040 --> 00:37:27,640
Just in case.

643
00:37:28,840 --> 00:37:29,840
In case of what?

644
00:37:34,080 --> 00:37:35,240
In case...

645
00:37:35,960 --> 00:37:37,280
I have to use my right hand.

646
00:37:38,560 --> 00:37:40,520
-So your left hand--
-It's fine.

647
00:37:45,600 --> 00:37:47,080
Don't tell them about me

648
00:37:47,640 --> 00:37:49,000
practicing with the right hand.

649
00:37:52,640 --> 00:37:54,040
[exhales heavily]

650
00:37:57,120 --> 00:37:58,240
-[grunting]
-[thwacking]

651
00:38:02,440 --> 00:38:04,840
-[clicking]
-[clanging]

652
00:38:06,240 --> 00:38:07,400
-[thumps]
-[gasps]

653
00:38:08,080 --> 00:38:09,320
Even you are being difficult.

654
00:38:10,120 --> 00:38:11,080
[Jiale sighs]

655
00:38:13,680 --> 00:38:14,520
Hm.

656
00:38:17,640 --> 00:38:18,880
